## Note  


Turning the front cam one graduation changes the toe- in about \(2.3mm\) {0.11 in} and the camber about \(13^{\circ}\) . Turning the rear cam one graduation changes the toe- in about \(2.3mm\) {0.11in} and the camber about \(8^{\circ}\) .  


3. Adjust the camber.  



